This file is the single source of truth for:

Which tables each analytics collection can query
Column descriptions (so LLM knows what data is available)
Per-persona, per-table row-level filter rules

The filter strings use Python .format() placeholders: {emp_id} and {dept}. These are resolved at runtime with the authenticated user's actual values.

